Tell him, and spare not.
Look, what I have said, I will avouch ’t in presence of the king; I dare adventure to be sent to th' Tower.
Tis time to speak.
My pains are quite forgot.
Thou killed’st my husband Henry in the Tower, And Edward, my poor son, at Tewkesbury.
I was a packhorse in his great affairs, A weeder-out of his proud adversaries, A liberal rewarder of his friends.
To royalize his blood, I spent mine own.
Were factious for the house of Lancaster.— And, Rivers, so were you.
Was not your husband In Margaret’s battle at Saint Albans slain?
Let me put in your minds, if you forget, What you have been ere this, and what you are; Withal, what I have been, and what I am.  
